# 📚 DokBook – Docker-Based Book Registry System

DokBook is a lightweight web-based application for managing book records, built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and containerized using Docker. This project allows users to add, edit, view, and delete book entries in a simple and interactive way.

## 🛠 Features

- Add new books with relevant details
- View a list of all registered books
- Edit existing book information
- Delete books from the registry
- Dockerized deployment for portability and consistency

